title: Nordo in for PA! Lagos/Gorg/PA/Micheletti
description: Eric Nordquist fills in for Paul Allen on the final day of PA's vacation! Sporting Director of Minnesota United Manny Lagos calls in to talk about the Loons, Kevin Gorg joins the show to talk Twins, Canterbury, and Wild, Paul Allen talks with Nordo about his vacation as well as his upcoming show at the Zimmer ranch, and Pat Micheletti is in studio to talk all things hockey and more!
